reviewText:
police car in the pursuit of justice arrived back on January 17 2012 anybody who loves police cars will enjoy this DVD is has police cars from the Indiana state police the Missouri highway patrol and Michigan state police it also the 1996 Michigan state police vehicle tests also Ed sanow
the head of the missouri highway patrol and the fleet of new 1996 Chevrolet caprices and more.
Is the history but stays history.  Wish this video would have also included more about today's cars and how we got to this point.  Gets a bit on the boring side.
